<i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ualysiaofscynthia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alysia of Scynthia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 338<br> <font color=#993300>(4/10/02 1:39:41 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=226.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> A Visitor</span><hr size=1> Alysia's head gaurd came knocking at the hut. She had long blonde hair and wore short leathers much like her Queen.<br><br>She looked inside the hut and spotted the woman. Not many of the sisters knew why the Queen had taken this amazon into their village, knowing everything that had happened. But Alysia found an old scroll in one of her boxes that read:<br><br>&quot;I, even I, am he who blots out <br>your transgressions, for my own sake, <br>and remembers your sins no more.&quot;<br><br>Alysia herself did not know where it came from, or how it got there, or even what it really meant. But she believed that she should learn mercy on others. Though Samsara did not know this mercy thing, Alysia knew it greatly.<br><br>The woman, Nicala looked to this new amazon and then spoke:<br><br>&quot;Vasilissa Alysia-Samsara wished for me to tell you that we are feasting in the main of the village at High Moon if you wish to join us.&quot;  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=genesisdtiberon>Genesis D Tiberon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#993300>(4/10/02 2:00:00 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=226.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.monkeegirl.com/rpg/genny.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A Visitor</span><hr size=1> As the Amazon entered she got to her feet quickly, sorrta tilting her head to her.  She wasnt very tall maybe 5ft 2 or so, she noded to the girl<br><br>"Sure, id like to join you..thank you"<br><br>She seemed nervous..something was bothering her and she asked politly<br><br>"Is everything ok in the village?"<br><br>She felt as if something was near..something icky. <p><IMG SRC="http://www.monkeegirl.com/rpg/genbanner.jpg"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uwarriorgabrielle.showPublicProfile?language=EN>WarriorGabrielle</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#993300>(4/10/02 7:32:30 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=226.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Brewing storm.</span><hr size=1> Gabrielle had been in seclusion for sometime - away from everyone, but pending news could not keep her away for long.  Word of Genesis arrival into Amazon lands had worried her.  Something was not right, she had to find out. <br><br>Upon reaching the village she found out even more to make her dread an oncomming &quot;storm&quot; .. word of her daughters prescence in Amazon territory gripped her heart in fear.  It could mean nothing could would come of it.<br><br>Gabrielle snuck her way quietly towards what she believed to be Gens hut.  Crouching low by the window, her suspicion was confirmed upon seeing Gen with Nicala.  She waited till Nicala left and then quickly rushed into Gens hut closing the door behind her.  <br><br>&quot;Genesis?&quot;.... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uwarriorgabrielle.showPublicProfile?language=EN>WarriorGabrielle</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#993300>(4/10/02 7:33:48 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=226.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Oops</span><hr size=1> (Sorry guys, second paragraph is reffering to &quot;Hope&quot; if I confused anyone!::smiles innocently::) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=genesisdtiberon>Genesis D Tiberon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#993300>(4/10/02 3:06:57 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=226.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.monkeegirl.com/rpg/genny.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Gabby!</span><hr size=1> Genesis turned to Gabby and her eyes widened a bit. She didnt look like the Genesis Gabby last saw several months ago. Her soft bownish blonde hair fell to her shoulders as blue eyes blinked. <br><br>"Gabby!"<br><br>She ran over and gave her a big hug! Her actions and movments everything about her seemed human once more. It was almost odd, to see such a thing.<br><br>"I missed you so much!"<br><br>She backed away looking her over with a smile<br><br>"how have you been? and whats going on out there?"<br><br>walking to the window as she spoke looking up at the sky. By the look in her eyes, she knew something was coming, just couldnt place what <p><IMG SRC="http://www.monkeegirl.com/rpg/genbanner.jpg"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uwarriorgabrielle.showPublicProfile?language=EN>WarriorGabrielle</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 4<br> <font color=#993300>(4/10/02 7:33:17 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=226.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> A Storm is Comming</span><hr size=1> Gabrielle returned Gens hug thankful she was alright.  <br><br>&quot;I heard rumors.. ones I hoped wern't true, but they are..&quot;<br><br>She pulled Gen to look out the window and into the darkening skies.  There was a storm brewing, though no rain fell.. a faint chilling breeze could be felt amidst the gloom of the stillness.<br><br>&quot;It's been getting darker and darker since I arrived.. its like no storm I've ever seen.&quot;  She then turned her gaze upon Gen.  &quot;And you, you look so different... so much more.. well.. human..&quot;  A faint smile played across her lips as she patted Gens cheek, before gazing once more outside.<br><br>&quot;We had better find Alysia, she may have an idea of whats going on if we dont.&quot; <br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=genesisdtiberon>Genesis D Tiberon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 4<br> <font color=#993300>(4/10/02 8:16:50 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=226.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.monkeegirl.com/rpg/genny.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A Storm is Comming</span><hr size=1> She cocked a brow at Gabby..more human? The look is as if she never looked anything but human? She shrugged it off drawing her attention back outside<br><br>"Aly might, yeah"<br><br>She absently fiddled with her hair as she pondered with a sigh <p><IMG SRC="http://www.monkeegirl.com/rpg/genbanner.jpg"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ualysiaofscynthia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alysia of Scynthia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 340<br> <font color=#993300>(4/11/02 1:50:44 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=226.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Tribal Feast</span><hr size=1> The feast had begun and in the main hall, the amazon tribe gathered. Amazons were still questioning many things that had been happening as of lately.<br><br>Alysia nodded to Nicala as she took her place standing behind the Queen. Alysia looked to the others.<br><br>&quot;We are here to feast as sisters, we must learn to love oneanother as sisters. Remember, there is no such thing as a Rogue Amazon in my eyes. Without a tribe, an amazon is merely a woman looking for a cause to live.&quot;<br><br>She looked to the others briefly as they spoke of Genesis. The rumors of Saurians comming back were still a mist, however, the Scynthian army was never as strong. And with the new assistance of Queen Raven of Tanias River Valley, nothing would kill the Tretmolecs ever again. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=genesisdtiberon>Genesis D Tiberon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 5<br> <font color=#993300>(4/11/02 2:06:29 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=226.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.monkeegirl.com/rpg/genny.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Tribal Feast</span><hr size=1> she realized the time and without word ran out her hut door to join Aly and the others. She stopped a ways off from them, but close enough she could be seen clearly. She suddenly found herself nervous.. her wolf hearing allowed her to hear what they were saying..she hesitantly went to Aly trying not to draw attention to herself<br><br> <p><IMG SRC="http://www.monkeegirl.com/rpg/genbanner.jpg"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ualysiaofscynthia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alysia of Scynthia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 341<br> <font color=#993300>(4/12/02 1:44:21 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=226.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Tribal Feasting</span><hr size=1> Alysia nodded to Gen as she approached the others. She then motioned to an empty seat and then cast her eyes to the others.<br><br>&quot;We gather tonight to celebrate sisterhood in the greatest way. We are all united in blood. The blood that was shed from our foremothers the Tretmolecs.&quot;<br><br>She sighed lightly remembering those times.<br><br>&quot;We have a great enemy out there, we have many battles ahead of us throughout all time, so right now we gather together celebrating our peaceful times, and our triumph over the world of men!&quot;<br><br>She rose her chalice to the others.<br><br>&quot;The Amazons will live Forever!&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=genesisdtiberon>Genesis D Tiberon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#993300>(4/12/02 2:51:40 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=226.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.monkeegirl.com/rpg/genny.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Tribal Feasting</span><hr size=1> She nodded back to Aly as she took a seat..she was a bit uncomfrotable. As Aly made her toast she listened carefully...and found herself fealing like a proud mother as she watched her.<br><br>Genesis then looked down, going over everythng in her head from the moment she woke up in the forest to now, and it all seemed more odd. She shook it off and looked up once more to Aly and smiled <p><IMG SRC="http://www.monkeegirl.com/rpg/genbanner.jpg"></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showPrevMessage?topicID=226.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showNextMessage?topicID=226.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=226.topic&index=11><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/addReply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.emailToFriend?topicID=226.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm6.threadControl?topicID=226.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator 